'''Sidi Ḥraẓm''' iga yan iɣṛm illan g [[Lmɣrib]] g tmnaḍt n [[Fas]]. iḍfaṛ Sidi Ḥṛazm itɣrmt n Fas, 12 Km sg wammas ns. G usggas n 2014 illa g Sidi Ḥṛazm 5622 n ufgan. 

== Assaɣ ==
Assaɣ n sidi Ḥṛazm ittyusmma f yan udm bahra ittuyssan g igr n ttaṣwwuf g tusut tiss 12, udm ad assaɣ ns igat Ɛali ibn Ḥaṛazim.

